#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:2 0837b0051e184b688b663133596c2836
msgid "ML Datasets"
msgstr "机器学习数据集"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:4 cc396c92e5e84a63b4da88c8fa2f9836
msgid ""
"Three scripts in ``examples/dataset/`` generate large, ML-ready batches of "
"PDE solutions for training neural operators (GAOT, FNO, Transolver, …). The "
"recipe is the one outlined in :doc:`../user_guide/batched_workflows`: same "
"mesh, many right-hand sides, one factorization, multi-RHS back-substitution."
msgstr ""
"``examples/dataset/`` 中的三个脚本生成大规模、可直接用于机器学习的 PDE "
"解批量数据，用于训练神经算子（GAOT、FNO、Transolver 等）。其方法即 "
":doc:`../user_guide/batched_workflows` 中所述：同一网格、多个右端项、一次分解、多右端项回代。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:10
#: 41ee36f615f04f36864cf2256bfc640a
msgid ""
"``poisson/poisson_dataset.py`` — 1000 steady-Poisson samples over random "
"source fields, on a circular domain; the cleanest illustration of factor-"
"once / back-sub-many."
msgstr ""
"``poisson/poisson_dataset.py`` —— 在圆形区域上、对随机源场生成 1000 个稳态泊松样本；这是\"一次分解 / "
"多次回代\"最简洁的示范。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:13
#: 966fda9cdb3d4319b1731e37e97e2dad
msgid ""
"``heat/heat_dataset.py`` — 1000 heat-equation samples, 100 timesteps, on an "
"L-shaped domain."
msgstr "``heat/heat_dataset.py`` —— 在 L 形区域上生成 1000 个热方程样本，每个 100 个时间步。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:15
#: 62ed2ad5dffc4b6fbcb8d8f949759fd9
msgid ""
"``wave/wave_dataset.py`` — 1000 wave-equation samples, 100 timesteps, on a "
"circular domain."
msgstr "``wave/wave_dataset.py`` —— 在圆形区域上生成 1000 个波动方程样本，每个 100 个时间步。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:18
#: 8780969aabf244deaf0e31f4cacc0dd2
msgid ""
"These three datasets are used in the GAOT paper (`arXiv:2505.18781 "
"<https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.18781>`_)."
msgstr ""
"这三个数据集用于 GAOT 论文（\\ `arXiv:2505.18781 <https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.18781>`_\\"
" ）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:21
#: 9bc7b11c0f9a4f1b9fd1033da1f98ebc
msgid ""
"All three run on GPU when one is visible, fall back to SciPy on CPU, and "
"benchmark the two paths against each other. The headline is how **cheap** "
"this is: because the system matrix is factored only once and every sample — "
"and, in the transient cases, every timestep — is just another right-hand "
"side, generating a 1000-sample dataset costs barely more than a single "
"solve. The timings below tell the story: 1000 steady Poisson solves in half "
"a second, and 1000 transient runs of 100 steps each (a hundred thousand "
"linear solves) in about ten seconds on a single GPU."
msgstr ""
"当有可见的 GPU 时，这三个脚本都在 GPU 上运行，否则在 CPU 上回退到 SciPy，并对这两条路径进行相互基准测试。重点在于它有多 "
"**廉价**\\ ：由于系统矩阵只分解一次，而每个样本——在瞬态情形下，每个时间步——都只是另一个右端项，因此生成一个 1000 "
"样本的数据集，其代价仅比单次求解略多一点。下面的耗时说明了一切：1000 次稳态泊松求解只需半秒，而 1000 次各 100 "
"步的瞬态运行（十万次线性求解）在单块 GPU 上约需十秒。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:33
#: db87565a86954ad4854a9acaab964c17
msgid "Poisson batched RHS — ``poisson_dataset.py``"
msgstr "泊松方程批量右端项 —— ``poisson_dataset.py``"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:35
#: 996b574d4ddd4930ad1a78741a6d0c81
msgid ""
"The steady-state warm-up: one stiffness matrix, many source fields. The "
"script meshes a disk (radius :math:`0.5`, centered at :math:`(0.5, 0.5)`, "
"``chara_length=0.008``), draws 1000 multi-frequency Fourier source fields "
"from :class:`~tensormesh.dataset.PoissonMultiFrequency` (``K_modes=16``), "
"and solves all of them against a single assembled ``K``."
msgstr ""
"稳态热身：一个刚度矩阵，多个源场。脚本对一个圆盘进行网格剖分（半径 :math:`0.5`\\ ，圆心在 :math:`(0.5, 0.5)`\\ "
"，\\ ``chara_length=0.008``\\ ），从 "
":class:`~tensormesh.dataset.PoissonMultiFrequency`\\ （\\ ``K_modes=16``\\ "
"）抽取 1000 个多频傅里叶源场，并针对单个装配好的 ``K`` 一并求解。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:42
#: d3cf765130c342c4a59970e3d1885fe5
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The one Poisson-specific trick is the right-hand side. For a nodal source "
"the load :math:`\\int f\\, v_i\\,\\mathrm{d}x` equals :math:`M f` with the "
"mass matrix from the same quadrature, so the whole batch of loads is a "
"single sparse matmul ``M @ f.T``:"
msgstr ""
"唯一针对泊松问题的技巧在于右端项。对于节点源，载荷 :math:`\\int f\\, v_i\\,\\mathrm{d}x` 等于 :math:`M "
"f`\\ ，其中质量矩阵来自相同的数值积分，因此整批载荷就是一次稀疏矩阵乘 ``M @ f.T``\\ ："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:47
#: 3f60837e3bae41eb94edc963affcb516
msgid "examples/dataset/poisson/poisson_dataset.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/dataset/poisson/poisson_dataset.py（核心部分）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:74
#: 518aa05ac0e54198a0935645f9326a72
msgid ""
"The 2D RHS shape ``[n_inner, batch]`` is auto-routed to a direct solve: one "
"factorization, ``batch`` back-substitutions. The script asserts ``M @ f.T`` "
"matches the per-sample ``FAssembler`` load before solving, and cross-checks "
"the GPU result against an independent CPU re-assembly."
msgstr ""
"二维右端项的形状 ``[n_inner, batch]`` 会被自动路由到直接求解：一次分解，\\ ``batch`` 次回代。脚本在求解前断言 ``M"
" @ f.T`` 与逐样本的 ``FAssembler`` 载荷一致，并将 GPU 结果与一次独立的 CPU 重新装配进行交叉验证。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:80
#: 1aa2274bdc6b4ef1a3701ae94ce6d777
msgid ""
"On an NVIDIA RTX PRO 6000 (14478 DOFs total, 14145 inner, 1000 samples), all"
" 1000 solves finish in half a second:"
msgstr ""
"在 NVIDIA RTX PRO 6000 上（共 14478 个自由度，其中 14145 个内部自由度，1000 个样本），全部 1000 "
"次求解在半秒内完成："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:94
#: c4a62cb89caa4ac38964b52dc481f563
msgid ""
"Five representative samples from the generated dataset — the FEM Poisson "
"solution on the disk for five random multi-frequency source fields. The "
"script writes ``poisson_dataset.npz`` (solutions, sources, points, "
"coefficients) alongside this figure."
msgstr ""
"从生成的数据集中选取的五个代表性样本——圆盘上、对应五个随机多频源场的 FEM 泊松解。脚本会在生成该图的同时写出 "
"``poisson_dataset.npz``\\ （解、源、点、系数）。"

