#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:132
#: df2e8b6a4082460ca578c6931b602323
msgid "A few details that make the GPU path fast:"
msgstr "让 GPU 路径变快的几处细节："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:134
#: ce638eb17ded487c991deee516df7567
msgid ""
"``F`` is a 2D tensor at every step; the sparse matrix-multiplication ``M @ "
"U`` broadcasts over the batch axis on GPU."
msgstr "``F`` 在每一步都是二维张量；稀疏矩阵乘 ``M @ U`` 在 GPU 上沿批次轴进行广播。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:137
#: fa503867b2fe42dd908abff6c77209d4
msgid ""
"``K_.solve(F_)`` with ``F_`` shape ``[n_inner, batch_size]`` routes to "
"``torch-sla``'s batched-RHS direct-solve path (``K_`` is a "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix`, so ``.solve`` is the inherited "
"``torch_sla.SparseTensor.solve``). On CPU this is SciPy's LU; on GPU it is "
"cuDSS — a Cholesky factorization here, since :math:`M + \\Delta t\\, D^2 A` "
"is SPD. One factorization is reused across all 1000 samples and all 100 "
"timesteps."
msgstr ""
"``K_.solve(F_)``\\ （其中 ``F_`` 形状为 ``[n_inner, batch_size]``\\ ）会路由到 ``torch-"
"sla`` 的批量右端项直接求解路径（\\ ``K_`` 是 :class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix`\\ "
"，因此 ``.solve`` 是继承自 ``torch_sla.SparseTensor.solve`` 的方法）。在 CPU 上这是 SciPy 的 "
"LU；在 GPU 上则是 cuDSS——这里是 Cholesky 分解，因为 :math:`M + \\Delta t\\, D^2 A` 是 SPD "
"的。同一次分解在全部 1000 个样本和全部 100 个时间步上被复用。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:145
#: 7e3097030f354b5b84adf06d2695e4c5
msgid ""
"The L-shape is meshed at ``chara_length=0.008``, giving about 14k DOFs — "
"large enough that the batched direct solve dwarfs 1000 independent per-"
